I was given an appointment at Tue 9-10am. Arrived at around 9.15am. At the registration they give me Q number 45. I waited for almost 2hrs but the Q number is still on no. 16 and very very slow moving. I decided to go already cos I am starting to not feel well due to my condition of having a chest pain. Too crowded and I hope theres more Doctor to accomodate all patients.

And please when you send an appointment time, kindly follow it! Noted that theres too many brothers on that timing/day but please FOLLOW on the timing that you have given! You are misleasing your patients! Will NEVER come to this medical center again! VERY VERY FAR!!!!
Very good service and medical treatment
